    <bug_when>2017-06-14 12:16:42 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>It seems some changes related to the terminal flash were in at least three different ncurses snapshots: 20161126, 20161217, 20161231. It&apos;s not just a fflush() call in _nc_flush(), there are also changes in various terminfo files adding a delay.

As this bug was apparently present for a number of years and until now there were no complaints, I&apos;m not sure if it alone warrants an ncurses update in F25. With more bugs we can reconsider.

In any case, it&apos;s already fixed in F26.</thetext>
  </long_desc>
      
      

